OL,6,FFIFA has confirmed a 10-month
OL,7,Fworldwide ban for Newcastle United's
OL,8,FSandro Tonali.
OL,10,FIt means the midfielder has been
OL,11,Fruled out of Saturday's Premier
OL,12,FLeague clash with Wolves after FIFA
OL,13,Fhas ratified the ban.
OL,15,FThe Italian Football Federation
OL,16,F(FIGC) announced on 26 October that
OL,17,Fthe 23-year-old had been suspended
OL,18,Funtil next season after agreeing a
OL,19,Fplea bargain as part of an
OL,20,Finvestigation into illegal betting
OL,21,Factivity.
